 1380+1380=2760 元，不是精确数据，但是幅度相差不会太大，主要在每年的利率变化和城乡居民基础养老金（增加幅度不大，不是每年都增加，每次增加十块二十块）的变化。<br /><br />农村人太苦辣 🥵", "last_modified": 1782866949, "replies": 189, "id": 1224086}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1778522847", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1778522847", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 12607, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1778522847", "stars": 1358, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 621675, "username": "xiaofangcode", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaofangcode", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/764108d877c77c2a6e3f09393f4f30b7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/764108d877c77c2a6e3f09393f4f30b7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/764108d877c77c2a6e3f09393f4f30b7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1680169219, "last_modified": 1782874555, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "tomorrowan", "last_touched": 1782889347, "title": "[bytecat]v 友赛博领鸡蛋 claude，新用户留言送 10 刀，十楼抽奖还送 10，中奖率 20%", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224145", "created": 1782874813, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 好久没来拉新了\r\n\r\n网址： https://www.bytecatcode.org/\r\n\r\n最近 v 站中转站越来越多，我们这边还是保持原来的节奏：稳定 + 性价比。\r\n\r\n老用户应该有印象，我们算是比较早一批在 v 站做推广的中转站之一。从 26 年 1 月建站到现在，一直没怎么折腾过大起大落的玩法。\r\n\r\n售后这块目前也还行，到现在总共就两单退款，而且基本都是当天处理完。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n# 当前分组价格\r\n\r\n- 福利分组（ Claude ） → 0.1x  \r\n- AWSQ → 0.4x  \r\n- Hyper → 0.68x  \r\n- Max → 1.35x  \r\n- Codex → 0.2x  \r\n- Codex-Pro → 0.4x  \r\n- Gemini → 0.8x  \r\n\r\n更多分组可以去官网看，价格是实时