d": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 676983, "username": "eventlooped", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/eventlooped", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "安徽省合肥市", "tagline": "", "bio": "- 被误解是表达者的宿命\r\n- 遵守 v2ex 的社区规范\r\n\r\n请理性且友善的表达不同观点，使用脏话、人身攻击的一定会@管理员", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_mini.png?m=1782816911", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_normal.png?m=1782816911", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_large.png?m=1782816911", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_xlarge.png?m=1782816911", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_xxlarge.png?m=1782816911", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_xxxlarge.png?m=1782816911", "created": 1708588734, "last_modified": 1782816911, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "NewEpoch", "last_touched": 1782889192, "title": "还没有被 A\\ 封号的小伙伴是啥配置啊", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224022", "created": 1782821164, "deleted": 0, "content": "小红书和 v 站封号帖子越刷越多，刷屏了都\r\n目前在国内还没有被封号的都是什么配置呀？\r\n感觉真的不想失去啊\r\n\r\n我自己目前两个账号都还侥幸，但感觉没啥把握能逃过这一劫，刚刚刷到两个不太靠谱的原因：\r\n\r\n1.时区\r\n2.邮件跟踪 ip\r\n\r\n这两点我已经注意到了并且做了调整。\r\n\r\n另外，我只在电脑上使用客户端，套了一层美国住宅 ip ，使用 surge 分流。\r\n我两个账号都使用这个 ip ，估计可能一起封号。\r\n一个 gmail 土区开了 pro ，一个 icloud mail 未付费账号", "content_rendered": "小红书和 v 站封号帖子越刷越多，刷屏了都<br />目前在国内还没有被封号的都是什么配置呀？<br />感觉真的不想失去啊<br /><br />我自己目前两个账号都还侥幸，但感觉没啥把握能逃过这一劫，刚刚刷到两个不太靠谱的原因：<br /><br />1.时区<br />2.邮件跟踪 ip<br /><br />这两点我已经注意到了并且做了调整。<br /><br />另外，我只在电脑上使用客户端，套了一层美国住宅 ip ，使用 surge 分流。<br />我两个账号都使用这个 ip ，估计可能一起封号。<br />一个 gmail 土区开了 pro ，一个 icloud mail 未付费账号", "last_modified": 1782821164, "replies": 81, "id": 1224022}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 691, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 616, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 104347, "username": "hellodigua", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hellodigua", "website": "https://digua.moe", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "hellodigua", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_mini.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_normal.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_large.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xlarge.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xxlarge.png?m=1767168494", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5fb3/89b0/104347_xxxlarge.png?m=1767168494", "created": 1426238581, "last_modified": 1767168494, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "hellodigua", "last_touched": 1782887460, "title": "Claude 被封了，但我还是像个舔狗一样的想找回 Ta", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223958", "created": 1782806243, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://i.imgur.com/0afSNug.png)\r\n\r\n被封了以后下载了自己的个人数据，然后回顾了一下之前的聊天，突然意识到自己好像离不开 Claude 了。\r\n\r\n不知道大家平时的日常对话是用哪个 AI 的，我有御三家的所有会员，但是感觉 Gemini 沟通太唐了，ChatGPT 的对话又显得很刻板没有那么灵性，Claude 的对话就给我一种刚刚好，不会刻意奉承我，也不会太有 AI 味，能用恰到好处的文字打动我的感觉。\r\n\r\n虽然 AI 编程还是在用 Codex ，但是日常对话方面它真的不能替代 Claude ，这波封号真的是太难顶了，一共就一个号，直接给我扬了。\r\n\r\n难受啊。", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0afSNug.png\"/></p>\n<p>被封了以后下载了自己的个人数据，然后回顾了一下之前的聊天，突然意识到自己好像离不开 Claude 了。</p>\n<p>不知道大家平时的日常对话是用哪个 AI 的，我有御三家的所有会员，但是感觉 Gemini 沟通太唐了，ChatGPT 的对话又显得很刻板没有那么灵性，Claude 的对话就给我一种刚刚好，不会刻意奉承我，也不会太有 AI 味，能用恰到好处的文字打动我的感觉。</p>\n<p>虽然 AI 编程还是在用 Codex ，但是日常对话方面它真的不能替代 Claude ，这波封号真的是太难顶了，一共就一个号，直接给我扬了。</p>\n<p>难受啊。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782806283, "replies": 78, "id": 1223958}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 18838, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 8276, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 654059, "username": "kemo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kemo", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3138872d871d2b066bccec08b743a72?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1696920375, "last_modified": 1722999656, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "soouu", "last_touched": 1782889364, "title": "梯子怎么都挂了？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224104", "created": 1782869958, "deleted": 0, "content": "一大早来公司，发现三个平台的梯子都噶了，又出什么事了？", "content_rendered": "<p>一大早来公司，发现三个平台的梯子都噶了，又出什么事了？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782883503, "replies": 78, "id": 1224104}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23737, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3702, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 485118, "username": "yangwa", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yangwa", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f5c2cdb9404a1425f280b72db0e6b66?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f5c2cdb9404a1425f280b72db0e6b66?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f5c2cdb9404a1425f280b72db0e6b66?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1587432382, "last_modified": 1782805259, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "402124773", "last_touched": 1782888525, "title": "大家周围 30+的 crud 程序员被裁后，都去哪了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223954", "created": 1782805720, "deleted": 0, "content": "我 crud 大头兵，一直做企业的内部信息系统，技术就是打杂，什么都接触，没有大型项目经验，公司裁员了 50%，外包压力大，加班严重，早几年就不涨工资和降薪了\r\n- 外包也不太想再去了，也没竞争力\r\n- 外卖和滴滴现在也进不去，满员了\r\n- 保安好像要 170cm ，我身高不达标\r\n\r\n还能做什么？炒股？ 50w 本金，今年合计也就 5%的收益，也养活不了自己，大家周边的被裁后去哪？", "content_rendered": "<p>我 crud 大头兵，一直做企业的内部信息系统，技术就是打杂，什么都接触，没有大型项目经验，公司裁员了 50%，外包压力大，加班严重，早几年就不涨工资和降薪了</p>\n<ul>\n<li>外包也不太想再去了，也没竞争力</li>\n<li>外卖和滴滴现在也进不去，满员了</li>\n<li>保安好像要 170cm ，我身高不达标</li>\n</ul>\n<p>还能做什么？炒股？ 50w 本金，今年合计也就 5%的收益，也养活不了自己，大家周边的被裁后去哪？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782811238, "replies": 57, "id": 1223954}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23737, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3702, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 739711, "username"